Description: Solutions for vibration, noise and harshness
Full Description: HyperDamping is revolutionizing the world of sound and vibration damping with proprietary and patent-pending technology. HyperDamping stops vibration, shock, and noise by combining material science with structural engineering to create a superior damping system.  Vibrations and shocks cause noise and damage to consumer electronics, vehicles, aircraft, building and gym floors, industrial equipment, and other everyday products. Existing solutions trade-off damping ability against weight and cost. HyperDamping eliminates that trade-off by utilizing the principles of structural mechanics to create cost-effective, lightweight, and extreme damping properties in elastic materials.
